			  			<HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  			Ok. Throughout the entie game, there is that info bar at the top that displays your PP, # of Planets, and Population. I think it would make more sense if it only displayed your Power, PP, and # of Fleets. This would prove to be more useful. <br />
<br />
I'm always having to go to the main page and check my power to see if an action made my power fluff to much or not. That, and if you see the # of Fleets change while your doing something else you would be alerted of an attack.<br />
<br />
What practical use does someone get from constantly knowing how many planets and population he/she has?<br />
<br />
Just a thought. It would be pritty cool to see a change.<br><p>-Kaebora Quaizar						<P align=right> </P>
